name: Chromasto Avikosni
description: From the creative works of mass graven image, produced by hand within Krita on GNU Linux public license. This work was all together about 22 hours in the making start to finish. the image is  purely abstract although familiar shapes and silhouettes can appear to stand out as it can produce pareidolia effects in some views. This work and all minted works are all original by Joshua Thomas AKA Mass Graven Image from Austin Texas.
